Text: great comix, im almost in love in that cat :)
Very fun comic book series. Just curious, but do you happen to have issues #50-52, the Backward Masking issues? I've been looking around everywhere and can't seem to find them.

"The One You Love" is 6 comic issues put together for some reason. I extracted all the files and separated them all into single issues. It's a great read and this storyline got me into Catwoman. You can get the entire series here:

http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/6290528/Catwoman

It's version 2.
